Package: kvkapiR
Title: An R Wrapper for the Dutch Chamber of Commerce API  
Version: 0.0.0.9004
Authors@R: 
    person("Coen", "Eisma", , "coeneisma@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-9001-2572"))
Description: Provides a convenient interface to the Dutch Chamber of Commerce (KvK) API.  
    This package is built using the `httr2` package and follows best practices  
    for wrapping APIs in R, as outlined in the httr2 documentation  
    (https://httr2.r-lib.org/articles/wrapping-apis.html). It simplifies  
    authentication, request handling, and response parsing when interacting  
    with the KvK API.
